1. "On čeka*š svoju priliku da ti pokaže svoju ljubav." (He is waiting for an opportunity to show you his love.)

2. "Ona je čekala* da se vrate kući." (She was waiting for them to come home.)

3. "Da li čekaš* da se vidiš sa njim?" (Are you waiting to meet with him?)

4. "Ja čekam* konačan odgovor." (I am waiting for the final answer.)

5. "On čeka* da čuje tvoj glas." (He is waiting to hear your voice.)